CODE EXAMPLES
One excellent example beats many mediocre ones 
Choose most relevant language: 
Testing techniques → TypeScript/JavaScript System debugging → Shell/Python Data processing → Python 
GE: 
Complete and runnable Well-commented explaining WHY From real scenario Shows pattern clearly Ready to adapt (not generic template) 
Don't: 
Implement in 5+ languages Create fill-in-the-blank templates Write contrived examples 
You're good at porting - one great example is enough. 
